quote><br />\n<br />\n新project以前會係香港做, 家下香港都無埋, 返左日本做, 係舊既project先會拎返去支那做, 根本無得防, 要抄出街一個月已經有老翻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國廠佬肯買有啤兩種顏色膠既機？！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有左N年啦, 你睇下支牙擦大把雙色啤左十幾廿年, 唔係咩新科技黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啤機邊值錢架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c9a5f36fefc85d6f58ea0e203328eb7ba12c88","tid":309940,"uid":122997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都唔明咁垃圾都有人玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為唔係中國製造</blockquote><br />\n上年定前年中國開左廠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLEGO保密好撚勁係支那開左廠之後成日有流出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有D唔係圖流出係成件人仔/件流出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一直都係支那做左10幾年都有, 係香港廠黎, 果時講間廠都3萬幾人, 係中山定珠海, 唔係好記得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁其實啤膠呢d下欄工序,咁係去d有咁平得咁平地方做。(遲d去埋印度巴基斯坦做)"},{"pid":"9d8a007cecd75317e75f2f25bddcbad84ca4222e","tid":309940,"uid":33730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:11:46.000Z","msg":"細個覺得幾舊水買盒LEGO好貴..<br />\n大個覺得搵地方擺佢地仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9db92e62c0e16c8e640d2d2e6361fe0d553fca","tid":309940,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都唔明咁垃圾都有人玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為唔係中國製造</blockquote><br />\n上年定前年中國開左廠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"